import React from 'react';
import { Navbar, Nav, Container, NavDropdown} from 'react-bootstrap';

const Header = () => {
    return (
        <header>
            <Navbar bg="light" expand="lg">
  <Navbar.Brand href="#home">Vivokal</Navbar.Brand>
  <Navbar.Toggle aria-controls="basic-navbar-nav" />
  <Navbar.Collapse id="basic-navbar-nav">
    <Nav className="mr-auto">
    <NavDropdown title="Categories" id="basic-nav-dropdown">
        <NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.1">Blogs</NavDropdown.Item>
        <NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.2">Local Dealers</NavDropdown.Item>
        <NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.3">Famous Food</NavDropdown.Item>
        <NavDropdown.Divider />
        <NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.4">Close</NavDropdown.Item>
    </NavDropdown>
      <Nav.Link href="#home">Home</Nav.Link>
      <Nav.Link href="#link">Products</Nav.Link>
      <Nav.Link href="#link">Sign IN</Nav.Link>
      <Nav.Link href="#link">Feedback</Nav.Link>
    </Nav>
    
  </Navbar.Collapse>
</Navbar>
        </header>
    )
}

export default Header
